_sText:
A medium small map centered around a set of office suites.  The map has 32 spawns and about 30 megs worth of custom content

The CT must escort a single hostage from their spawn to the other side of the map to win the round.  This was original designed as an AS_ map(that version will be released soon) so the layout isn't 100% ideal for hostage .nav routes but it works well enough.

All custom content is embedded into the .bsp
